T02:31:27.000Z","msg":"薪酬趨勢調查委員會公布今年公務員的加薪淨指標，低級是3.13%、中級是5.08%、高級是4.58%。按慣例，中低級公務員的加薪幅度，將會看齊，換言之，若建議獲通過，加幅將劃一為5.08%，高級公務員加幅是4.58%。<br />\n <br />\n3個淨指標是分別以薪酬趨勢調查得出的總指標，扣減今年遞增薪額開支後而得出，薪趨會下周會再開會，確認有關指標，最後向政府遞交的加薪建議。<br />\n<br />\n薪酬趨勢調查委員會主席李鑾輝表示，今年調查參考了108間私人公司、共16萬僱員的薪酬，認為是有足夠代表性，反映市場實際情況。<br />\n<br />\n今年各級公務員加薪幅度都較上年高，李鑾輝說，若今年數據屬理想及準確，相信職方代表會收貨。<br />\n<br />\n牛官又羸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746e90174d0fcd802784cc1eeadd83c7c874e44c","tid":1156851,"uid":36262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f401dc10569390d0e2fb553b18e5350ecbb52498","tid":1156851,"uid":186814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:08:28.000Z","msg":"硬撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504e4e88c1ce23f45bddcaa136db64fc19eb5af1","tid":1156851,"uid":36262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ddf96b6e2d2abda82aa951e4ef74def5fbd106e","tid":1156851,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:24:50.000Z","msg":"排隊入多汁地產"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:34:38.000Z","msg":"juicy ho fung so<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535b39337477b922ec35531ef104764fbc3d739b","tid":1156851,"uid":186814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e1b1cd02cffb741a713d6d0dc17ed871f3523df7","tid":1156851,"uid":196959,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:45:04.000Z","m